th for the remaining call site:\n\n- Uses `ArgsAndValue.class.getDeclaredMethod(\"class$\", String.class)` and invokes the compiler-generated resolver directly.\n- Passes a missing class name to force `ArgsAndValue.class$(...)` to execute its internal `Class.forName(String)` and convert the resulting `ClassNotFoundException` into `NoClassDefFoundError`.\n- Keeps the test scoped only to `io.restassured.internal.MapCreator$ArgsAndValue`.\n\nI did not run compilation or tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3a259b09eb7f87016a009bb0f34881948731d8ee65d4904b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 621, "output": 903, "cacheRead": 53760, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 55284, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778424738092, "responseId": "resp_0b3a259b09eb7f87016a009ba2f65881948b251b500982b360"}, "toolResults": []}
